              Oceananigans.Advection.upwind_biased_product(u⁺, c₊ᴸ, c₊ᴿ)
    Ax_ρuc⁻ = Oceananigans.Operators.ℑxᶠᵃᵃ(i,   j, k, grid, one(FT)) *
              Oceananigans.Operators.Axᶠᶜᶜ(i,   j, k, grid) *
              Oceananigans.Advection.upwind_biased_product(u⁻, c₋ᴸ, c₋ᴿ)

    return Ax_ρuc⁺ - Ax_ρuc⁻
